"= black, high values = white) or with a pseudocolor algorithm that "
"assigns colors to the values. Single band rasters with a palette can also"
" be drawn using the palette. Multiband layers are typically drawn by "
"mapping the bands to RGB colors. Another possibility is to use just one "
"band for drawing."
msgstr ""

